 <!-- Introduction -->
 <!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application resource for the
     representation of risk.
   </p>
   <p>
     The aspects of risk management, whether positive or negative, that
     result in an opportunity for benefit or threat to it succeeding
     are included.
   </p>
   <p>
     The risk_schema identifies risks with their probability and consequences
     pertaining to events or situations.  
   </p>
  </purpose>

